    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Python基础"><a href="#Python基础" class="headerlink" title="Python基础"></a>Python基础</h1><h2 id="安装python"><a href="#安装python" class="headerlink" title="安装python"></a>安装python</h2><p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/qq_53280175/article/details/121107748">超详细的Python安装和环境搭建教程_python安装教程-CSDN博客</a></p><h2 id="输出语句"><a href="#输出语句" class="headerlink" title="输出语句"></a>输出语句</h2><p>打印代码</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&gt;&gt;&gt; print(&quot;Hello World&quot;)</span><br><span class="line">Hello World</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="Python解析器"><a href="#Python解析器" class="headerlink" title="Python解析器"></a>Python解析器</h2><p>python解析器<br>    将Python代码翻译成计算机认识的0和1并提交计算机执行 在解释器环境内可以一行行的执行我们输入的代码<br>也可以使用解释器程序，去执行py代码文件<br>“.py”文件是什么？</p><p>python语言的代码文件，里面记录了python的代码<br>Python解释器程序在 python.exe</p><ol><li>创建test.py文件</li><li>向里面写入东西</li></ol><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">print(&quot;中国万岁&quot;)</span><br><span class="line">print(&quot;打到日本注意&quot;)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="3"><li>cmd执行  python test.py</li></ol><h2 id="下载pycharm"><a href="#下载pycharm" class="headerlink" title="下载pycharm"></a>下载pycharm</h2><h2 id="注释"><a href="#注释" class="headerlink" title="注释"></a>注释</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 单行注释</span><br><span class="line">&quot;&quot;&quot;&quot;&quot;  多行注释</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="变量"><a href="#变量" class="headerlink" title="变量"></a>变量</h2><p>变量：在程序运行时，能储存计算结果或能表示值的抽象概念。</p><p>语法:</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">变量名 = 变量值</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>print打印多条语句</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">print(&quot;&quot;,money)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="数据类型"><a href="#数据类型" class="headerlink" title="数据类型"></a>数据类型</h2><p><img src="http://img.caicablog.top/img/image-20231208093838396.png" alt="image-20231208093838396"></p><p>查看数据类型</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">type(&quot;&quot;)</span><br><span class="line">type(变量)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p> 数据类型转换</p><p><img src="http://img.caicablog.top/img/image-20231208093913396.png" alt="image-20231208093913396"></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">int(&#x27;11&#x27;)</span><br><span class="line">float(&#x27;3.2&#x27;)</span><br><span class="line">str(11)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="运算符"><a href="#运算符" class="headerlink" title="运算符"></a>运算符</h2><p>算术运算符</p><p><img src="http://img.caicablog.top/img/image-20231208094157511.png" alt="image-20231208094157511"></p><p>复合运算符</p><p><img src="http://img.caicablog.top/img/image-20231208094229432.png" alt="image-20231208094229432"></p><h2 id="字符串"><a href="#字符串" class="headerlink" title="字符串"></a>字符串</h2><ol><li>字符串的三种定义方式：<ol><li>单引号方式</li><li>双引号方式</li><li>三引号方式</li></ol></li><li>引号的嵌套<ol><li>可以使用：\来进行转义</li><li>单引号内可以写双引号或双引号内可以写单引<br>号</li></ol></li></ol><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">s1 = &quot;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">s2 = &#x27;&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">s3 = &quot;&quot;&quot;&quot;&quot;&quot;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">s4 = &quot;\&quot;我是中国人\&quot;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">s5 = &quot;&#x27;我也是中国人&#x27;&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>字符串拼接</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">s1 = &quot;1&quot; + &quot;2&quot;</span><br><span class="line">s3 = &quot;1&quot; + name+&quot;3&quot;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>占位拼接</p><p>字符串：%s<br>整数： %d<br>浮点数：%f</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">name = &quot;fklajlk %s&quot; % 10</span><br><span class="line">print(name)</span><br><span class="line">name = &quot;fklajlk %s fjkaj %s&quot;  % (10,30)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
